 - This map is created for gaining CSS achievements. CT bots are coming to the windows. There are special zones which give you infinitie ammo. The buttons at the left and right will kill bots.
- End the central button will teleport them to the swimming pool
- Join T and set the Deathmatch Mode. Also you can find a room for relaxing.


- Have fun
